{"tid":909641,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"倪匡:前幾年我靠某種植物既葉既幫助，聽到好多莫名其妙既聲(2)","createTime":"2018-11-20T14:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T14:06:09.000Z","uid":12152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b737f87e8e4e882f34e729db4de764799abbbe8a","tid":909641,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"羅大佑果part:19:30開始<br />\n當中談音樂創作 亦有表演彈唱 好精彩<br />\n跟住由貝多芬講到用心靈聽音樂<br />\n倪匡就分享佢試某種植物既葉既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先不討論對與錯 佢地幾個都無所顧忌繼續傾談<br />\n而又成功播出街<br />\n重點係:<br />\n今夜不設防係當時1989-1990既年代係電視播出既大熱節目<br />\n節目當中食煙飲酒又間中語言輪姦女嘉賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我相信打後既香港社會已經冇可能再有咁自由豪放既訪談節目出現<br />\n依家實有好多道德團體投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話香港自由冇倒退 我就真係唔信啦<br />\n其他集數都好多好精彩:張國榮 劉培基 林燕妮 等等<br />\n有興趣既巴打自己去J<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UVsBjEguyzo?t=1167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUVsBjEguyzo%3Ft%3D1167&d=P2blVT4FruhkJzLPvbqYUv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=83fadc63\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UVsBjEguyzo?t=1167</a><br />\n開係娛樂台好似錯錯地 所以開番係度"}]}